Sentencas: In this study, we fabricated thin-film solid oxide fuel cells supported by nanoporous substrates in order to enlarge an active area of the fuel cells.
Titulo: Fabrication of the large area thin-film solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The multilayered structures using sputtering and atomic layer deposition were utilized to form dense and defect-free electrolytes to prevent the gas leakage and electrical shortage.
Titulo: Fabrication of the large area thin-film solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The fabricated cell with the active area of 25 mm(2) showed the open circuit voltage of similar to 1.1 V and the maximum power density of similar to 100 mW/cm(2) at 500 degrees C.
Titulo: Fabrication of the large area thin-film solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The sheet resistance of the electrode became critical for fabrication of the thin-film solid oxide fuel cells with the large active area.
Titulo: Fabrication of the large area thin-film solid oxide fuel cells
